1
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:57,360
Tell me.

2
00:00:58,040 --> 00:01:00,040
If I post the videos of you cheating on exams,

3
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:01,120
bullying at school,

4
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:02,320
and shoplifting at the mall

5
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:04,160
in your dad's work group chat,

6
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,680
will he still be able to keep his job?

7
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,900
Please don't, bro.

8
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,780
We were just joking with Bai Qing.

9
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,570
We are all good friends.

10
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,660
Then write it down.

11
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,440
Write down everything you did

12
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:20,960
in detail,

13
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,360
and submit it to the school tomorrow.

14
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:25,000
If I don't hear anything by tomorrow afternoon,

15
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,000
all three of you will be expelled.

16
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,280
Don't run away,

17
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,720
you bad students.

18
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,759
I don't care how powerful your families are.

19
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:33,560
It's useless.

20
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,620
Write it right now.

21
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,479
I'll write it.

22
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,800
Be sincere.

23
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,460
Brother, you are amazing.

24
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,160
I didn't expect

25
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,040
you could really help me deal with those people.

26
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,000
Brother, I promise you.

27
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,000
I will definitely study hard and get into a good university,

28
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,130
and not let you down.

29
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,960
But actually,

30
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,639
it was Su Wan, Zhu Junchi,

31
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,639
and Ding Shiyu who helped you with this.

32
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,840
You had some misunderstandings with them before.

33
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,640
I hope you won't take it to heart.

34
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,640
Also.

35
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,640
Alright.

36
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,700
They are your friends.

37
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,680
I'll be polite to them.

38
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,000
Also,

39
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,320
I don't want my own sister

40
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:31,610
to have a misunderstanding with the girl I like most.

41
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,280
Brother, I have to do my homework.

42
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,079
You can go and do your own things.

43
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,920
Okay, get back to work.

44
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,200
I'll head out too.

45
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,920
Why contact me all of a sudden?

46
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,520
Have you thought it through?

47
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,079
Yes.

48
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,260
I have thought it through.

49
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,520
You did all of this.

50
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,800
You contacted the media.

51
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,570
You made the anonymous report.

52
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,080
You're just jealous that Tianyu is better than you,

53
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,400
so you want to ruin him.

54
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,240
Do you think by doing this,

55
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,760
you can be with me?

56
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,640
Are you begging me to let him off?

57
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:18,960
Sure.

58
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,240
Then be my girlfriend.

59
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:35,680
Eat.

60
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,800
Su Wan, how could you...

61
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:48,940
Choose Pinyin.

62
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,040
Su Wan, are you out of your mind?

63
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,400
Do you know why I like Tianyu

64
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,400
and not you?

65
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,320
Because he is upright

66
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,800
and responsible.

67
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:08,840
As for you,

68
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,400
you are dark and despicable.

69
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,330
You don't even deserve to be human.

70
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,160
By the way.

71
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,800
We will definitely find evidence to expose you.

72
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,320
Su Wan, I'm warning you.

73
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,180
Don't you dare!

74
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,640
I have recorded everything.

75
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,040
A scumbag like you

76
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,400
who is cruel and evil,

77
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,840
it's impossible to like you.

78
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,370
I wouldn't even look at you.

79
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,600
Do you think

80
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,930
saying a few harsh words

81
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,800
will make things better?

82
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,200
Don't be so proud, Su Wan.

83
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,240
Just you wait.

84
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,280
I'll wait then. Who's afraid of who?

85
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,080
Why are you here?

86
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:01,160
To thank you.

87
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,880
Thank me?

88
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:06,760
Thank you for solving the trouble for Bai Qing.

89
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:10,960
And thank you for coming up with a solution for the garage.

90
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,160
Most of all, thank you

91
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:15,080
for choosing me as your love experiment subject.

92
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,000
Thank you for standing up for me.

93
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,930
And thank you...

94
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:19,080
Alright,

95
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,520
that's enough.

96
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,040
So,

97
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,160
are we still friends?

98
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,480
Of course.

99
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,160
Then as a friend,

100
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:32,240
I don't think Gao Chenyang is suitable for you.

101
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:32,720
Gao?

102
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,159
That's ridiculous.

103
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:37,159
How could I possibly choose him?

104
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,450
But I clearly saw...

105
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,690
Are you talking about the cafe?

106
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,760
I was teaching him a lesson, okay?

107
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,520
Didn't you see I took a glass of water

108
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,720
and threw it right in his face?

109
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,680
He was petrified.

110
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,810
But I want to say,

111
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,840
you're not allowed to see him alone again.

112
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,240
He's a dangerous person.

113
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,920
If someone needs to teach him a lesson,

114
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,920
it should be me.

115
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,840
Are you worried about me?

116
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,400
Well,

117
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:09,800
what else?

118
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,360
Hello, Mom.

119
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:28,680
Su Wan,

120
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,120
Such a big thing happened,

121
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,600
and you didn't even tell me.

122
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,480
How long are you going to hide it from me?

123
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,360
Come back right now.

124
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:37,360
Okay, I got it.

125
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,280
I'm going up then.

126
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,159
Bye.

127
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:59,100
You didn't tell me about such a big thing.

128
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:01,480
Do you think your mother can't handle it?

129
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,480
No.

130
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,200
Mom,

131
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,840
are you still willing to help us?

132
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,360
Tell me,

133
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,400
what exactly happened?

134
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,240
It's like this.

135
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,040
That night,

136
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,740
he blocked me in the alley.

137
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,330
There was no one around.

138
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,720
I thought I was dead.

139
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,880
Fortunately, my friend Yuding passed by and saved me.

140
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,120
I didn't expect him to keep harassing me,

141
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,360
and even cause trouble for my friends.

142
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:31,200
He reported his auto repair shop to the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

143
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,200
It's all my fault.

144
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:33,680
If it weren't for me...

145
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,340
You're really pissing me off.

146
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:41,010
I'll help you contact a friend at the law firm.

147
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,770
But we have to find the evidence ourselves first.

148
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,560
Su Wan,

149
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:47,180
can you not keep things from me in the future?

150
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,040
Just tell me directly, okay?

151
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,280
Gao Chenyang, you bastard!

152
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,760
I'll beat you up every time I see you.

153
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,560
You uneducated jerk,

154
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,160
you antisocial psychopath.

155
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:03,400
Gao Chenyang!

156
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,000
My lady,

157
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,080
you've been at it all night

158
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,940
with just these two lines.

159
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,720
Can we talk about something constructive?

160
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,600
You think I'm nagging.

161
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,160
Not really.

162
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:29,960
If you're my bro, curse with me.

163
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:33,200
Gao Chenyang, you bastard!

164
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,200
Miss, stop making a scene. Sociopath,

165
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,919
come down quickly.

166
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,860
Stop embarrassing yourself.

167
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,720
Come down.

168
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,440
I'm sorry.

169
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:04,280
I didn't mean to take advantage of you.

170
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,360
You're a girl.

171
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,760
I should be the one saying that.

172
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:13,760
Whatever.

173
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:19,200
Gao Chenyang, you bastard!

174
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,200
Ding Shiyu, oh, Ding Shiyu.

175
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,120
Yelling here for 300 years

176
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:31,160
won't solve the problem.

177
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,160
I say just give Gao Chenyang, that bastard,

178
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,680
10,000 yuan and be done with it.

179
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,880
Let him help clarify.

180
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:38,080
It's not big money anyway.

181
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,160
As long as it keeps

182
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,080
you guys

183
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,600
safe

184
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,600
and happy, that's enough.

185
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,760
Is it a matter of money?

186
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,560
It's a matter of justice, dignity,

187
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,320
and the truth, okay?

188
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:55,720
Sister,

189
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,760
do you have some hero complex?

190
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,760
That's still better than you being rich and stupid.

191
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,520
It's better than you only knowing how to use brute force,

192
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:01,920
tigress.

193
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,680
It's better than you only knowing how to use money,

194
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,540
nouveau riche.

195
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,840
Do you know

196
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,280
that if you do this,

197
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,200
they'll just think we are guilty

198
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,000
and anxious to keep them quiet?

199
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,400
Then we'll never be able to clear our names.

200
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,640
Can't you use your brain?

201
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,040
This time, I'll admit you make sense.

202
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,480
But you...

203
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:36,440
Look at your tolerance, lightweight.
